'''''Spaceguide''''' was a publication of the [[Bureau of Scouting and Exploration Services|New Republic Scout Service]] issued to new [[Scout/Legends|scouts]]. It gave its readers a taste of the lifestyle they were about to embark upon and provided advice intended to assist scouts in successfully completing their missions.

